  <brief_title>Counterpulsation Reduces Infarct Size Pre-PCI for AMI</brief_title>
  <acronym>CRISP-AMI</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Controlled Study of Mechanical Left Ventricular Unloading With Counterpulsation to Reduce Infarct Size Pre-PCI for Acute Myocardial Infarction - CRISP AMI</official_title>
