  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Subjects with anterior acute STEMI who receive an IABC before primary PCI will have decreased
      MI size.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Post clearance device study in which subjects with acute MI will be randomized 1:1 to either
      receive IAB or to receive standard of care without IAB before mechanical reperfusion.
      Subjects will be followed throughout their hospital stay and at 30 days.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
